        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "It is enough, my Lord, enough indeed;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "My strength is in Thy might, Thy might alone."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "This is the hour of banquet and of song;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "This is the heav’nly table spread for me;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Here let me feast, and, feasting, still prolong"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The brief bright hour of fellowship with Thee."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Too soon we rise; the symbols disappear;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The feast, though not the love, is past and gone;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The bread and wine remove, but Thou art here,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Nearer than ever still our Shield and Sun."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Feast after feast thus comes and passes by,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Yet passing, points to the glad feast above,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Giving sweet foretastes of the festal joy,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The Lamb’s great bridal-feast of bliss and love."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
